{"tid":2013472,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"劉細良講幾句啱聽既嘢就信到十足，連登仔真係入世未深。","createTime":"2020-05-12T10:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T10:47:50.000Z","uid":219007,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"df68a51f163a3b14367d53b1638fde44a408657f","tid":2013472,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:17:08.000Z","msg":"當年所謂本土論述其實都係好普遍嘅嘢，喺其他地方根本就正常不過。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">只不過係香港特別唔同嘅係有班離地中產+泛民，先至顯得「本土」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。  <br />\n<br />\n所以本土在地主張一定係成為主流，當年已經有一班人係咁講。 無論毓民、練乙錚、鄭立、李怡、本民前、熱狗等等仲有一大班網民都明白同埋理解。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但當年日日俾你呢班友批評係鬼，係收共產黨錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又呢個係鬼，嗰個係鬼。 原因都係得一個：影響了佢哋政黨利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好啦～捉鬼捉咗咁耐，係2019年<span style=\"color: red;\">一班平時唔理呢啲嘢嘅民眾</span>受到感動，全力支持勇武抗爭，亦都證明佢哋唔抗拒「本土派」同本土主張，<span style=\"color: red;\">於是乎佢地見勢色唔對，一夜之間就轉晒風向，係連解釋都冇一個，道歉亦都冇一句。<br />\n</span><br />\n咁有啲人會話「<span style=\"color: red;\">佢有進步唔得嘅咩？！有進步唔係好事咩？！</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n進步？喂～唔好唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係前一兩個禮拜，係前一兩個禮拜咋！</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一眾區議員、立埸姐姐同大班連登仔都要求泛民內會拉布不能縮沙，皆因泛民往續同政壇消息指有部份議員怕DQ，最後成功迫使泛民投名狀拉布到底。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成功體現選民監察議員職責。係有公權力嘅人受到民主監察！</span><br />\n<br />\n結果俾佢話你地中左計，因為咁做客觀係分化左泛民。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1998618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1998618</a><br />\n<br />\n最好笑係四月嗰陣佢哋自己講話適當嘅監察同埋批評係需要！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n所以從呢一件事上 可以睇到<span style=\"color: red;\">當 人民民主利益 同 泛民政黨利益 有衝突嗰時，佢係會揀後者。</span> 跟住佢同你講佢係支持民主同尊重民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n學毓民話齋：<span style=\"color: red;\">政黨只不過係工具，國家人民先係目的。係民主社會，人民係對政客永遠都存在質疑，係唔會有任何感情。 </span><br />\n<br />\n隔左六至七年之後，到佢講返當年比佢話係鬼嘅人講返同一句說話，連登仔就當佢神咁拜。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇咁撚蠢呀你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最最最最</span> 起碼 係咪都要同多年俾你捉過係鬼親本土派人士同組織等等道過歉呢？係咪～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就係因為一大班之前冇留意開呢啲嘢嘅人，今日開始留意，結果唔知歷史，盲頭烏蠅，周圍撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醒少少啦 DLLM <br />\n<br />\n根據呢班人往續，只能夠解釋因為選舉近了，做拉攏下你哋渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n死傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffd0f7f30c658d1f5406a9eb11273fc95881ceb","tid":2013472,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1444bd70a759a2a5e2a1ac0c8ba3042075b42b4d","tid":2013472,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6360fddc44dede06682b1bc8da138dfa84ecffeb","tid":2013472,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104daa02ef3c5b05be9ac93b75e837e9d492e703","tid":2013472,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c01db6191983aec35ae59f45d8211705b44f25","tid":2013472,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34d7dc23b269025788290dc9aad05c965ab2371","tid":2013472,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142db866cde058967488ef4c5ac2d06f2f7b0ce3","tid":2013472,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3278771df32a88e62213ec705ee5c94c30d7c7d0","tid":2013472,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾熱狗，拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔聽細良都聽攬炒啦，仲搞分化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e61f0ca2ef0f0ea1d624f0e8503a98f471e6548","tid":2013472,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:21:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n一直都係勇武主角<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"3b9cb877d6a7e3cf39bd040419d085c0126102e4","tid":2013472,"uid":54415,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:23:19.000Z","msg":"未聽劉細良點講，但呢下係咪多少都將攬炒巴既概念帶俾中坑中產？"},{"pid":"8d563936e2f33b1d60a0a181bb1782ca8723c351","tid":2013472,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3278771df32a88e62213ec705ee5c94c30d7c7d0","tid":2013472,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾熱狗，拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔聽細良都聽攬炒啦，仲搞分化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"搞清楚先唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n適當嘅批評係絕對需要。 如果到呢一刻仲係為咗保住個位即係唔係攬炒，睇返而家有議席既泛民近排動向都唔足夠攬炒。<br />\n<br />\n而政黨政客都係人，人係會犯錯，而正所謂：人不為己，天誅地滅。 佢哋為份工為份糧好正常，但咁樣會同香港嘅民主運動背道而馳。 所以我哋好擔心未來就算有35+都唔足以攬炒。  <br />\n<br />\n而睇返劉細良往續，遠既不特止，淨係呢幾個月已經前後矛盾。 而客觀效果都仲係只係桿衛泛民政黨當選利益。<br />\n咁從民主角度，群眾對佢哋作出質疑同監察係好正常。<br />\n<br />\n欖炒巴都呼籲現有擁有議席嘅人應該唔能夠再做投降派啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38bae18a495d1f03c2c85df192a321d1c7f7caa","tid":2013472,"uid":275351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"已經無聽佢6個月。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b594b539feb17253ff2f97460f829c755114c8","tid":2013472,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:47:50.000Z","msg":"中產係會聽細良<br />\n但唔會睇你呢個post架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你不如去細良youtube channel留言仲快reach 到你要既target audience"}],"pinned":{"pid":"8d563936e2f33b1d60a0a181bb1782ca8723c351","tid":2013472,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"搞清楚先唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n適當嘅批評係絕對需要。 如果到呢一刻仲係為咗保住個位即係唔係攬炒，睇返而家有議席既泛民近排動向都唔足夠攬炒。<br />\n<br />\n而政黨政客都係人，人係會犯錯，而正所謂：人不為己，天誅地滅。 佢哋為份工為份糧好正常，但咁樣會同香港嘅民主運動背道而馳。 所以我哋好擔心未來就算有35+都唔足以攬炒。  <br />\n<br />\n而睇返劉細良往續，遠既不特止，淨係呢幾個月已經前後矛盾。 而客觀效果都仲係只係桿衛泛民政黨當選利益。<br />\n咁從民主角度，群眾對佢哋作出質疑同監察係好正常。<br />\n<br />\n欖炒巴都呼籲現有擁有議席嘅人應該唔能夠再做投降派啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}